        &kp ESC    &hm_l LALT A &hm_l LGUI S &hm_l LCTRL D &hm_l LSHFT F &kp G      &none           &kp LGUI   &none    &none   &kp LALT        &none    &kp H     &hm_r RSHFT J &hm_r RCTRL K &hm_r RGUI L &hm_r RALT SEMI &kp RET
