        &trans     &none      &kp BSLH   &kp POUND   &kp DLLR    &kp CARET                             &trans   &trans                           &none     &kp AMPS    &kp PIPE    &kp LBKT   &kp RBKT      &trans
        &trans     &trans     &none      &none       &none                      &trans      &trans     &trans   &trans  &trans    &trans                   &none       &none       &none      &trans        &trans
      >;
